summary: i have an analysis and y’all ain’t gonna like it.
body:
i have an analysis and y’all ain’t gonna like it.

right so i feel as if the phandom have kinda confined dan and phil from being who they really are. like regardless of sexuality, they still act really closed.

for example, you tubers such as joe sugg and caspar lee do jokes that involve more touchy stuff, yet i feel as though dnp don’t do that in fear that we instantly take it the wrong way.

i feel like we should take a step back a bit and then we might get content that you wanna see.

title: Interactive Introverts
body:
I went to Dan and Phil’s Interactive Introverts show in Providence last night by myself. I’ve been a huge fan of them since I was in high school (8 years ago now!) And, last night I fulfilled my teenage dream of seeing them in real life.

Now, if you want to see the show and you are an Introverted 21+ adult who has no IRL friends who like Dan and Phil, you should totally do it while you have the chance. D&P truly put on an amazing, entertaining show that can be enjoyed by all fans alike. Even though I am an older fan who went alone, last night was just the best night. I know I would have regretted it if I didn’t go when I knew I could. Please, if you are like me or are just a D&P fan in general, go see the show if you can!!!
